    • 方法详细资料

      • getMessage

        public static java.lang.String getMessage(java.lang.String packName,
                                          java.util.Locale locale,
                                          java.lang.String messageId,
                                          java.lang.Object... args)
        get message by message pack/persist name,locale,message id and arguments. it will check the IMessageContext, if user not call the method
        I18n.configurePackContext(IMessageContext messageContext) to set a message context;
        it will use the default message context BundleMessageContext
        参数:
        packName - String message pack/persist name
        locale - Locale special locale
        messageId - message key id
        args - message format arguments
        返回:
        String the final i18n message for the special locale

      • getMessage

        public static java.lang.String getMessage(java.lang.String packName,
                                          java.lang.String messageId,
                                          java.lang.Object... args)
        get message by message pack/persist name,Locale.getDefault(),message id and arguments.
        参数:
        packName - String message pack/persist name
        messageId - String message key id
        args - Object[] message format arguments
        返回:
        String the final i18n message for the default locale

      • getMessage

        public static <T extends IMessage> java.lang.String getMessage(java.lang.Class<T> entityClazz,
                                                               java.util.Locale locale,
                                                               java.lang.String messageId,
                                                               java.lang.Object... args)
        get message by message entity class type, locale, message id and arguments.
        it is best to use it as retrieve persist message from database.
        参数:
        entityClazz - Entity message class type
        locale - Locale
        messageId - String
        args - Object[]
        返回:
        String
